{"tid":158014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[血濃於水]拉丁女巴士喊「I hate Chinese」＋打人 成車中國人無出聲","createTime":"2017-03-16T03:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T06:43:35.000Z","uid":77196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbcd5dba3ef223128931ab4e5e9ccf7892a99dd","tid":158014,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;我恨華人!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n美國紐約發生辱華事件。一名拉丁裔美國女子在巴士大喊「I hate Chinese」（我恨華人），繼而持傘毆打車上一名中國老人洩憤。最讓人無奈的是，當時<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全車的中國人，沒有人出聲協助被毆的老人</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n美國紐約《每日新聞網》前日報道，當地時間上周二(7日)上午11時，一輛載滿華人的巴士行駛期間，一名身穿紅衣的拉丁裔美國女子站在司機門旁。她手持雨傘向車上的華人高喊「I hate Chinese」（我恨華人），更舉起中指。<br />\n<br />\n在該女子身旁的中國老人聽見，先用中文說：「這種族歧視啊!」，繼而嘗試用英語勸阻女子，但對方繼續辱罵，未幾更使用雨傘柄打向華翁頭部。老人問對方為何出手打人，女子回應稱「因為我恨華人」。<br />\n<br />\n受襲的老人事後坦言，「我感到很不舒服，我以為紐約是個友好的城市，有很多種族的人，我們在一起，非常好，非常平和。但現在，」老人指自己於1986年移民美國，喜愛紐約的多元文化，但從未遇上這類事情，對這次事件深感痛心和不安：「我知道他們當中有人恨中國人，我不得不小心一點了。」<br />\n<br />\n拍攝影片的女子在影片中表示：「很心寒，坐了一車的中國人，沒有一個人願意站起來幫助這個華裔老人。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170316/56435012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170316%2F56435012&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fb06189b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170316%2F56435012&h=f693f84c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170316/56435012</a>"},{"pid":"407b2463d1e8095579555523bfeb11acdb928dd4","tid":158014,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"打得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798763de0d701985e485de03d251498371525850","tid":158014,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"因為其他&quot;中國人&quot;都唔識英文. &quot; I hate Chinese&quot; 太深"},{"pid":"eb9979f6dbf7f31b284d5b872ecc9b5a3e7f7427","tid":158014,"uid":34229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為其他&quot;中國人&quot;都唔識英文. &quot; I hate Chinese&quot; 太深</blockquote><br />\n肓腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340dce6c2aeac5365c8d700a1e126fa1ad624b16","tid":158014,"uid":82381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:31:32.000Z","msg":"崇洋港人表示冇問題<br />\n冇人會批鬥佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4549e1a641c1118d401e16884c1027161caa4d3d","tid":158014,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:32:15.000Z","msg":"香港人既話會幫手打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b6f0fe00434f3c204377b416168fa914d43b8b","tid":158014,"uid":18809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"咪有個大陸女人衝佐出嚟叫停手囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f2c85b095bcb0f304edbc0d6335eed1dd70ed2","tid":158014,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"之前堆大陸人自己夠係咁"},{"pid":"1cd1c33d331892383728e79bea6e76064cc5f650","tid":158014,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"去到邊都一樣，支那人最無骨氣，最叻做陰濕野"},{"pid":"1d3425b321e7869ff6d781e79659ad7059fed724","tid":158014,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"I also ....."},{"pid":"1ceae53dd26a4a5edf1868a76b0a9d9897be2a45","tid":158014,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:45:02.000Z","msg":"其他嗰D可以係美國人黎<br />\n<br />\n外表既種族特徵似支那, 唔代表佢係支那人"},{"pid":"9457d672d724734c4baec17eab0ad47677a0d49a","tid":158014,"uid":79563,"lik